{"tid":359280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪我太小氣？","createTime":"2017-08-14T11:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T13:58:47.000Z","uid":121336,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"319dfc0e7c1f598358c9f74102886dd3d2f9f1db","tid":359280,"uid":121336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"公司識左兩個同事，<br />\n平時幾好傾而且差唔多日日都會一齊食飯，<br />\n本身當佢哋係朋友，<br />\n佢地生日都會請佢地食飯一齊慶祝，<br />\n點知到我生日就咩表示都無（明知係邊日），<br />\n其中一個連生日快樂都無句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我話我唔介意就肯定係假，<br />\n其實係咪我太小氣？<br />\n只係將心比心，<br />\n我覺得自己當人地係朋友，<br />\n但原來人地眼中我只係一個飯腳"},{"pid":"e4af78e6921caa567efa7e312c8d05ae00d891fc","tid":359280,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4204dddbdcda9dcfa4a447097d854c40a86233a3","tid":359280,"uid":130732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"人地撚知你約時生日咩 都話新朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0f8b8d425e1d73747aafbdc601f82519bd27c4","tid":359280,"uid":135879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:17:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9ad82f7cf4416a48f7874b7daaae45c552827fc","tid":359280,"uid":121336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地撚知你約時生日咩 都話新朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識左成年幾而且肯定知，我地都有假日約一齊出街之類"},{"pid":"b8369cbf5fdd8cccc421cae6c731e133e7370dd7","tid":359280,"uid":130732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地撚知你約時生日咩 都話新朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇漏字自膠左 <br />\n可能佢地冇點當你好好朋友掛"},{"pid":"fbad0cff817312b1cfe2d1240e6cdba7a505308d","tid":359280,"uid":121336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>公司識左兩個同事，<br />\n平時幾好傾而且差唔多日日都會一齊食飯，<br />\n本身當佢哋係朋友，<br />\n佢地生日都會請佢地食飯一齊慶祝，<br />\n點知到我生日就咩表示都無（明知係邊日），<br />\n其中一個連生日快樂都無句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我話我唔介意就肯定係假，<br />\n其實係咪我太小氣？<br />\n只係將心比心，<br />\n我覺得自己當人地係朋友，<br />\n但原來人地眼中我只係一個飯腳</blockquote><br />\n同事之交淡如水</blockquote><br />\n本來以為有例外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話曬大家年紀差唔多都算幾好傾"},{"pid":"81663a3aa955345b75cc12c18dd3b991605848c5","tid":359280,"uid":80107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"同事咋<br />\n平時幾好傾都只係同事<br />\n人地有自己生活圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f666fbca467c38d892f76aa4f6f601797efec574","tid":359280,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"諗起有個同事生日我地同佢食粥佢嬲左成個月唔講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc788afba6c5a704f3a16672a597644beb4f497","tid":359280,"uid":121336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同事咋<br />\n平時幾好傾都只係同事<br />\n人地有自己生活圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係既...原來自己太天真，本身無咩朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80eff035427f4df45ece31325d8e1eee792a9c49","tid":359280,"uid":121336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:21:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起有個同事生日我地同佢食粥佢嬲左成個月唔講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係咪都應該唔鬼再理佢地，好似好小家但又覺得自己條氣唔順"},{"pid":"4cee44496c4bfcf301a60e238917b3c9c185bc0c","tid":359280,"uid":121336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地撚知你約時生日咩 都話新朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇漏字自膠左 <br />\n可能佢地冇點當你好好朋友掛</blockquote><br />\n點解永遠都係我對人好我付出但咩回報都得唔到？<br />\n讀書開始就已經係咁"},{"pid":"44d43f691eaedf052b12a8885827613d0800dede","tid":359280,"uid":76754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"On9"}]}